Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.41,0:00:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憶往昔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德和哈里  抓鬼特工隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們屬于這里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是專業人員
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專業的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超自然事件調查
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.96,0:00:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這東西  它能使我們獲得一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名望  金錢  和姑娘...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾床單
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之間的一切問題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實都因為我們是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.05,0:00:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么  我們從此不再是家人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說既然你想好好合作  那就合作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說我們以后都公事公辦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的公事公辦是指你我之間的關系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那天說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你不在乎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.36,0:00:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能是沒考慮周全
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.11,0:00:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我那么做  是因為那是該做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并不是為了我而救我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是為了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.55,0:00:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fn方正黑体_GBK\fad(500,500)\b1\bord0\shad2\pos(193,233)\c&HE1DED9&}華盛頓州  斯普林代爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  你在家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,911  請問你有什么緊急情況
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我屋里有個人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能說出你的地址嗎  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.58,0:02:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士  請不要掛電話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開始追蹤你的電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得保持通話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請保持通話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會派警官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\bord0\shad1\fad(500,500)\fn方正准圆_GBK\c&H24EFFF&}兇鬼惡靈\N{\fs17\c&HFFFFFF&}第九季 第十五集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正水柱_GBK\fad(500,500)\bord0\fs22\pos(192,239)}{\c&HD2D2D2&}#瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華盛頓州  我找到一樁案子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要我一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去獵魔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么不去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你最近讓我找不到北
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  你想來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪現場流出的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩在自己房間被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門窗都鎖著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壁畫先生是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問得是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜  被拍下來的鬼魂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我像是要留下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fn方正黑体_GBK\fad(500,500)\b1\bord0\shad2\pos(193,233)\c&HE1DED9&}華盛頓州  斯普林代爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我洗了好幾個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還得把地毯扯下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女兒  凱茜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地毯的顏色還是她自己選的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請節哀  邁爾斯太太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說凱茜沒有什么敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你注意到發生過什么不尋常的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電路異常  燈閃爍什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視出毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什么問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有什么寒氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我想問一句
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什么要說到寒氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  聽起來一定很怪  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而警方一無所獲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不得不賣掉房子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雇傭私家偵探
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那些超自然論者打來電話時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超自然論者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道聯調局會覺得這不合常理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這些人知道別人不知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欠凱茜的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我至少要聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們提起寒氣的事是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是超自然現象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們今天會過來看一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些超自然論者告訴你他們叫什么了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}抓鬼特工隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓鬼特工隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真見鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊  我們又多了兩個粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  哈里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是我們那次圖書館的采訪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙計
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜又發了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她改了她的頭像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然裁過了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但能清楚地看到有個男人摟著她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而她還笑得那么開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許他們只是純潔的友誼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個摟著她的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫家兄弟  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-從沒有人  -這么覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閉嘴聽好  我們這么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.12,0:06:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個小丑  給我鉆進外面那輛破車里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后給我滾蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則我就打穿你們的膝蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們需要點什么嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以埋單了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張盤子上還有臟東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻去給我洗干凈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  特里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不怕你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我的槍打個招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在向我炫耀肚臍毛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是塞在褲子里的女槍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩者都有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你們怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要處理這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-沒錯  -是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我看到的是一對兒為名利忘乎所以的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著攝像機拍攝一個剛失去女兒的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙計們  我們是調查員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們完全有權利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你們沒有  知道為什么嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們只會礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者害死別的什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  你們要么識相點自己離開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么就爬出去  自己選
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶  你們能不能放松點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們心里有數
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-沒錯  -是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你們其他的隊員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個胖子哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有個女孩  有個女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們  我們不要他們了  他們是累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們絕對還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂了  現在就剩你們倆傻瓜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆不到五分鐘就會死在鬼的手里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們以為是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-絕對不是鬼  -不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  你們說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們覺得是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我來好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-行啊  -好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等這一刻等一輩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃癟吧  賤人們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會開槍斃了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賤人們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛剛說到  你們這就要走了  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,談話愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看他們是蛋白質吃多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}捉鬼特工隊  《瘦人揭秘》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德和哈里寫了本書
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《瘦人揭秘》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作者是美國最頂尖的超自然論者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這看上去的確像是凱茜·邁爾斯身后的那個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者被削掉臉皮的蓋思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兒呢  瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最早流傳于網絡的都市傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會在目標生活的背景中徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到他決定下手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網上的一切都是真的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如鯊魚襲擊直升機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也寫書講那個了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙計  不管是不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這網站上有幾千人發帖了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人好像是新的大腳怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許瘦人只是名字新奇的鬼魂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這么說是因為你真認為
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鬼魂還是單純因為你討厭捉鬼特工隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了  我們在凱茜屋里探測到了電磁信號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那房子旁邊有電線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會影響讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個女孩死在密室里  薩姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯然就是鬧鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許它在房屋上鎖之前進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢  迪恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎么可能世界各地的人們都看到了一樣的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼魂可不會到處跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在隔界里各種亂套
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼魂說不定能滿地出現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  迪恩  瘦人目擊事件幾年前就開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔界的問題只有六個月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還到處有人說看見貓王了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是說那倆二貨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:09:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是任何方面的專家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查當地死亡名單
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看有沒有誰可能是那個鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壁櫥  凱茜度過生命黃昏的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  伙計  別再用臉書
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟蹤你的前女友了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒說錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她把感情狀態改為"一言難盡"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰管呢  是你甩了她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩的一切都一言難盡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她拿到奶油松餅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還非要扔掉里面的餡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是松餅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  她的確挺有病的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好了嗎  -恢復狀態了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就要找到瘦人了  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能聞到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能聞到他的獠牙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從未如此接近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這事真的很嚴肅  哈里  -是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫家兄弟也來了  你也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被薩姆和迪恩打穿膝蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有考慮過或許我們該  別管這事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能讓那倆肌肉男搶走我們的榮譽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰管他們怎么想  他們連推特都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會找到瘦人的  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我們的家人  和唐娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是為了讓你前女友后悔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了讓所有黑后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪姬  斯布魯斯  那些逃兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想過什么"正常生活"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-去他們的  -太對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我們找到瘦人  是他們會上{\u1}《菲爾醫生》{\u0}嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}脫口秀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們會上《菲爾醫生》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  開始錄影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:11:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好了嗎  -嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個年輕女孩的閨房有兩個用處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡笑和快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人將歡笑變成流血
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在氣場太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你喜歡嗎  -真的很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有很多女人喜歡上這個的  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會需要通氣管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們將暢游在...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你們可能會渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  聽上去很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  過去六個月里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯普林代爾有三起非自然死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但都與凱茜·邁爾斯無關
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且都不是很慘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的事應該不會產生復仇鬼魂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有很多未解的死亡懸案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被歸為瘦人所為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人死了  幾周后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會發現死者的某張照片里有瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么瘦人是跟蹤狂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據傳聞是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是傻子這么說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎么沒注意到這些被害人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這些神秘死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以用非超自然原因解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些照片大部分看上去挺假的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括凱茜的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了凱茜的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱茜的照片沒有修改過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她身后的那東西真的是在那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這完全說不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世上怎么能有東西又真又假
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個女孩死了  這個絕對假不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她做的最后一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用手機照了相
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片怎么流傳到網上的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最早是發在一個瘦人粉絲網站上的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但IP地址卻查不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西還有粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么肯定有人希望照片流傳到網上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且肯定不是鬼魂上網發布的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警長在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想問他幾個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警長去打獵了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很感謝你們能來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是很需要幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你發現這個時它就被摔壞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  或許她失手掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,911電話在11點59時斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片發布的時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概凌晨2點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是驗尸官認定死亡時間是午夜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她是怎么用手機發布照片的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是超自然現象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什么這么說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幾個人來過  問了些關于這案子的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說他們可能能幫上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們給了我一本他們寫的書  關于...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:14:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}蘋果餐館
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探員  謝謝你們能來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個二貨在這兒干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得整點《靈媒緝兇》那套也沒什么壞處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我們隔兩個郡  大家在到處找一個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8月份失蹤的可憐的小男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方找了一個靈媒去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天就找到了尸體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有監控錄像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你們滾蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要把我趕出去嗎  "探員"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在犯罪現場玩狗仔隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了對你們  對其他人有任何益處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有博主  迪恩  那些信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些需要一些證明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確信瘦人的確存在的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是說網上有很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這個瘦人很死忠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那可不是  -當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.87,0:17:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果加上適當的西藏字符
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆蠢貨想沒想過瘦人變成幻像怪成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為幾千人對瘦人的描述是統一的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關于瘦人的傳言千變萬化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是幻像怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說廢話了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你們倆真的知道瘦人是什么嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我們只是在電視上扮演超自然論者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們完全不知道我們在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們當然知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人是半人半樹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人認為他來自一個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自閉癥男孩的惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說你們也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙計們  過來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么從停車場突然進入餐館的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門是鎖著的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錄像顯示特雷10分鐘前才鎖上的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖沒鎖都不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道瘦人能瞬間移動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的電磁探測器毫無反應
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許不是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二位探員也信這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-副警長  探員  干得好  -我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再看一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人把瘦人的餐館視頻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發在我們博客的評論區了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-誰啊  -管他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持速度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什么把忍者衣服穿上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能等到再出人命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚就要找到瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-在哪  -當然是林子里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太籠統了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據傳說  瘦人在樹旁邊出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而林子里都是樹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩起命案  他肯定在本地的林子里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩個人死了  真的死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是忘不了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許該讓薩姆和迪恩接手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先  絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再者  別再掃我的興了{\fs14}[在我的彩虹上下雨]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有雨就沒有彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用科學對付我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一種情感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能現在放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們馬上就能找到瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終于能彌補我們為了做這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而失去的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實交給專業人士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實也不是什么壞主意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是專業人士  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:19:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去樹林嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便哪片樹林  艾德  隨便
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是病急亂投醫  但說到瞬移
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想到"十字路口惡魔"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡捅人看視頻網站的惡魔  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  說起那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特里被刀捅死的視頻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經掛上網了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩千人看過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有人故意要讓大家看到瘦人行兇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為會有人看  因為那些人很變態
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么時候病毒視頻從小猩猩掉下樹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成殺手偷拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什么視頻會在網上瘋傳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只可惜那個沒留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你五歲時扮成蝙蝠俠的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從棚屋上跳了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你以為自己會飛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時九歲  而且我扮的是超人好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球人都知道蝙蝠俠不會飛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時不知道  摔斷了胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.51,0:20:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓你坐在我的車把上送你去了急診室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是快樂時光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很重要的事要告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后這案子就歸你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是哈里  一個人的抓鬼特工隊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在在樹林里調查潛在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人棲息地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤身一人  深入樹林
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.57,0:21:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離死亡之刃這么近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓人喪失理智
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:22:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運的是  我清醒得很
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.77,0:22:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做抓鬼特工隊  就專心一意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯布魯斯想辦公司
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.88,0:22:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪姬一心要玩輪滑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.82,0:22:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我憑什么阻止他們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.09,0:22:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是哈里  我不能讓他屈服于他的女友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說抓鬼特工隊很蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.17,0:22:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢  你們能相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不管
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她爸的對沖基金有多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.95,0:22:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能看著哈里變成公司的走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.87,0:22:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來像是碧池蒙德高中的悲慘時光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.87,0:22:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}取自電影Fast Times at Ridgemont High  雷奇蒙德的快樂時光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟案子有什么關系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里要離開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.87,0:22:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得給他一個留下的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我編造了瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人跟蹤被害人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但局勢反轉了  朋友們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.54,0:22:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟蹤狂變成了被跟蹤的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.27,0:22:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說這破事根本就是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:22:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一張管家的老照片  后期好好處理一番
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.96,0:23:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我匿名發在一個恐怖論壇上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.01,0:23:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就火了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.25,0:23:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只我們偽造了一件案子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.60,0:23:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們準備收拾東西回家時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.55,0:23:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在網上說見到了瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.16,0:23:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我們就去追查  后來瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.02,0:23:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就成了大眾傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.90,0:23:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是領頭羊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這感覺很奇妙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.77,0:23:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有追隨者的感覺很好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里  非常沉迷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.33,0:23:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德  你得告訴他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.56,0:23:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.50,0:23:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是追蹤瘦人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.54,0:23:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有瘦人  我們就是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.52,0:23:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是  蠢男
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.67,0:23:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.30,0:23:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我告訴哈里  他就會離開抓鬼特工隊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.16,0:23:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不告訴他  他還是會離開
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.93,0:23:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.36,0:23:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密會毀掉兩個人的關系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.89,0:23:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  等時機成熟我就告訴他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.81,0:23:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在時機就很好  伙計
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.44,0:24:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在樹林里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.93,0:24:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.95,0:24:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人  不管這是什么鬼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.41,0:24:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經殺死兩個人了  現在哈里又只身在樹林里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.60,0:24:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實算不上是樹林啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.57,0:24:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓他在雜貨店后面的幾棵樹邊下車了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.51,0:24:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  他不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.57,0:24:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙計們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.14,0:24:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  這是個  是個
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.61,0:24:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是個木棍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.29,0:24:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堆起來搭成的陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.95,0:24:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是瘦人留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.63,0:24:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.28,0:24:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.10,0:24:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.39,0:24:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.98,0:24:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兒還有其他東西
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.57,0:25:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太緊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.10,0:25:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.33,0:25:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我沒事  -好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.15,0:25:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我們回旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.94,0:25:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再好好處理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.32,0:25:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是對的  艾德  真有瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.01,0:25:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有新留下的胎痕
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.09,0:25:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我拍了照  -干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.09,0:25:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛車可能屬于割傷你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.02,0:26:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,割傷我的是瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.35,0:26:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人不開車
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.29,0:26:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是瘦人  混球
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.75,0:26:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用我一一給你們解釋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.42,0:26:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你倆都挺聰明的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.26,0:26:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.83,0:26:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.40,0:26:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前怎么不說
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.00,0:26:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.19,0:26:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你會生我的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.26,0:26:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得沒錯  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.85,0:26:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.22,0:26:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在非常非常生你的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.72,0:26:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.16,0:26:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你毀掉了我們的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.62,0:26:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來要結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.29,0:26:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我離開她  跟你東奔西跑  生活在謊言之中
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.69,0:26:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少咱倆都在
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.36,0:26:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.29,0:26:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我沒有編造瘦人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.20,0:26:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這會兒正做著無聊的工作  算著無聊的數字
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.35,0:26:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯唐娜爸爸之命是從
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.75,0:26:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我救了你  老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.21,0:26:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我  免于什么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.88,0:26:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免于過上好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.63,0:26:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免于不被刀捅傷
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.09,0:26:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還能再自私一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.42,0:26:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許現在還不晚
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.92,0:27:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以打給她試試
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.12,0:27:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-沒用的  -也許能行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.36,0:27:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的  想知道為什么嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.10,0:27:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經有個男人摟著她了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.88,0:27:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的狀態是"一言難盡"  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.14,0:27:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里  我們一開始并不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.58,0:27:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人是真是假
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.51,0:27:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我是有一些內幕
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.80,0:27:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我們是為了粉絲堅持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.01,0:27:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那跟以前有什么不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.95,0:27:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們又不會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.83,0:27:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.06,0:27:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我顏面盡失  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.79,0:27:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里  我們可以熬過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.60,0:27:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以揭穿瘦人的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.00,0:27:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后繼續抓鬼特工隊的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.04,0:27:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.44,0:27:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不能相信你了  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.70,0:27:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  哈里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.61,0:27:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白  你生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.16,0:28:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所說的話都不是出自真心
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.72,0:28:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里  告訴我你需要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.67,0:28:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去買咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.75,0:28:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以坐在這兒冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.52,0:28:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么樣
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.14,0:28:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.18,0:28:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.88,0:29:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺被人胖揍了一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.04,0:29:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都不是真的  薩姆
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.83,0:29:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德就是在裝模作樣  現在他還想要我假裝
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.76,0:29:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像這一切沒什么大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.54,0:29:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.71,0:29:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事你可以原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.54,0:29:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事不行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.13,0:29:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事算哪一種
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.31,0:29:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得自己考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.90,0:29:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胎痕找到匹配的了  如果你想...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.02,0:29:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.01,0:29:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種輪胎只有一種車用
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.48,0:29:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1989年的吉優都市
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.71,0:30:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這么小的鎮子  這車只有一輛
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.19,0:30:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官說是屬于一個叫羅杰的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.39,0:30:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在鎮子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.55,0:30:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北面的工廠做夜班保安
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.40,0:30:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西既可以瞬移  又有工作有車
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.33,0:30:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么情況
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.27,0:30:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.33,0:30:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆和迪恩有線索了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.00,0:30:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要去給你處理爛攤子了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.83,0:30:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得對  是我的爛攤子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.50,0:30:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該由我去處理
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.92,0:30:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只會越幫越忙
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.72,0:30:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.82,0:30:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不是沒拋下他們不管過
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.39,0:30:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在何必自找麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.25,0:30:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再做水母的脊柱了  哈里
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.53,0:30:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水母哪有脊柱
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.26,0:30:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.36,0:30:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心碎和謊言以前
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.19,0:30:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的出發點是幫助人  對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.22,0:30:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.35,0:30:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.36,0:30:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們沒道理不過去
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.33,0:31:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成我們主要的出發點
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.48,0:31:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里  我可以彌補這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.44,0:31:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以彌補這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.60,0:31:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是要跟我一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.37,0:31:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是說了  我和我的搭檔會處理這事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.11,0:31:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上司不在
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.37,0:31:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又沒有搜查令
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.67,0:31:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事出了岔子  我可就麻煩大了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.38,0:31:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  你在后面跟著就好
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.30,0:32:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想用用這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.27,0:32:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你就是瘦人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.36,0:32:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不是那么胖
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.93,0:32:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也倒能說得通了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.19,0:32:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶  薩姆  讓他住口
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.43,0:32:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.95,0:32:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么  諾伍德
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.74,0:32:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是惡魔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.61,0:32:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么瞬移進入餐館的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.18,0:32:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團隊合作
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.86,0:33:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒什么瞬間移動
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.81,0:33:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有幾個白癡在造謠生事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.77,0:33:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我認得你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.02,0:33:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那家餐廳的服務員
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.18,0:33:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  你就是想殺了你老板嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.26,0:33:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特里是個人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.13,0:33:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那凱茜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.57,0:33:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么惹你了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.59,0:33:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不愿意和我約會
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.57,0:33:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我用別的東西招呼她
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.48,0:33:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的刀子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.38,0:33:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好  羅杰
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.24,0:33:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來警長沒活著離開鎮子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.12,0:33:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該給我我要求的假期的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.37,0:33:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就為這個殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.87,0:33:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我誰也沒殺
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.63,0:33:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是羅杰殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.15,0:33:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個瘋子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.13,0:33:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我是個夢想家
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.84,0:34:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不怪你們輕視我
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.88,0:34:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都輕視我
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.90,0:34:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥氣的探員  來到這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.83,0:34:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就把我當成個小文員
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.37,0:34:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實我就是"瘦人"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.37,0:34:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那種感覺有多棒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.38,0:34:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  變態  我還真不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.16,0:34:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  帥哥是不會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.02,0:34:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人無視是什么感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.34,0:34:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一個只有三百人的小鎮長大
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.03,0:34:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是從沒有人注意過你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.59,0:34:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們看不見我們
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.07,0:34:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你倆是怎么認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.14,0:34:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過"瘋子網"嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.60,0:34:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.86,0:34:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是兩個呆子在一間空蕩蕩的酒吧相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.64,0:34:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一見如故
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.41,0:34:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和羅杰
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.09,0:34:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然都是陰謀論迷
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.39,0:34:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我們發現了"瘦人"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.24,0:34:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就轟炸了整個留言板
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.20,0:34:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這算什么  變態角色扮演嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.60,0:34:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真人扮演
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.28,0:34:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發博客是很有趣  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.71,0:34:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  讓我猜猜  你們想要更多
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.93,0:35:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道你們倆混蛋做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.05,0:35:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并沒讓你成為"瘦人"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.66,0:35:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們只能算是模仿犯
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.67,0:35:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是"瘦人"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.59,0:35:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你沒辦法告訴別人我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.05,0:35:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你馬上就要死透了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.19,0:35:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戲開場
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.90,0:35:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倆真是幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.79,0:35:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是我們目前為止最好的視頻的主演
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.09,0:35:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等視頻瘋傳
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.92,0:35:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都會知道"瘦人"是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.72,0:35:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備  開拍
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.11,0:35:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  別別別  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.27,0:36:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.38,0:36:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他踢到了我  這是報復
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.54,0:36:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是史酷比時刻  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.54,0:36:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}史酷比·杜  美國動畫片角色
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.92,0:36:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫下面具
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.28,0:36:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你不是瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.45,0:36:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是個"咪咪"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.51,0:36:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德  應該是{\u1}彌母{\u0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.51,0:36:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}文化傳播中起基因作用的媒介  泛指模仿者
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.34,0:36:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可拼寫是M-E-M-E
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.76,0:36:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二個E不發音
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.60,0:36:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是個咪咪  是個人類彌母
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.51,0:36:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我創造了你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.97,0:36:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝賜教
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.84,0:36:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我熱愛經典  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.36,0:37:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正處于《弗蘭肯斯坦》式的情節中
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.00,0:37:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然是我的創造者
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.89,0:37:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們本打算放你們中的一人一條生路
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.61,0:37:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來傳頌我們的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.27,0:37:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可現在
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.68,0:37:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你們都死了  就沒人能證明
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.90,0:37:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人是你們的創造
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.90,0:37:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.94,0:37:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開槍  不  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.91,0:37:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沖我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.28,0:37:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.75,0:37:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行嗎  都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.11,0:37:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我槍里的子彈足夠弄死你們倆了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.10,0:38:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-現場搞定了嗎  -是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.10,0:38:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人的錄像加上我擺放尸體的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.81,0:38:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該有足夠的線索讓別人以為
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.59,0:38:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兩個瘋子同歸于盡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.71,0:38:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們只是凡人  伙計
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.97,0:38:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不是惡魔  也不是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.67,0:38:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們  只是該死的凡人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.61,0:38:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  就像我說過的  人很變態
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.45,0:38:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我們沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.86,0:39:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我們不會和好如初了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.96,0:39:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們做出了彌補
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.56,0:39:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們打敗了那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.71,0:39:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我們抓鬼特工隊東山再起的好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.54,0:39:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你來這是為了解決瘦人的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.52,0:39:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是想結束一個篇章  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.86,0:39:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是要結束這整本書
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.43,0:39:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你剛救了我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.87,0:39:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺了人  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.12,0:39:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個壞蛋  哈里
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.87,0:39:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是個人  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.54,0:39:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太多人因為你的謊言喪命
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.07,0:39:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的謊言還不是為了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.69,0:39:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道為什么你看不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.11,0:39:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.68,0:39:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是為了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.32,0:39:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德  我可以原諒很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.30,0:39:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這事我無法原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.10,0:39:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們怎么辦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.23,0:39:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.37,0:40:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言難盡
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.33,0:40:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能載我一程嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.79,0:40:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.55,0:41:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里  你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.86,0:41:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.84,0:41:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說  不好
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.79,0:41:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和一個人一起混那么多年
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.92,0:41:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你甚至相信他會永遠和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.96,0:41:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像  等你老了  在門廊喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.10,0:41:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會坐在另一把搖椅上
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.79,0:41:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可之后發生了些事
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.97,0:41:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.24,0:41:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一把椅子上的人不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.19,0:41:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂我的意思嗎
